import React, { Component } from 'react' export default class Card extends Component { render() { const {con, date_depart, id_annonces, nombre_places, prix, ville_arrivee, ville_depart, time} = this.props.item let t =new Date(time.split("T")[0]+" "+time.split("T")[1].split("Z")[0]) console.log(date_depart) return (

{ville_depart}

{ville_arrivee}

{prix} DH
{new Date(date_depart).toLocaleDateString()}

) } }
